*Ručak* je uvek bio obeležen za moju porodicu. (Lunch has always been a special occasion for my family.)

Moje dete je obožavalo *ručkove*. (My child loved lunches.)

Uživala sam u *ručku* sa svojim prijateljima. (I enjoyed the lunch with my friends.)

Moj deda je spremao najbolji *ručak*. (My grandfather cooked the best lunch.)

*Ručkao* sam sa svojim kolegama. (I had lunch with my colleagues.)

Naše trpezarije su bile puna tokom *ručka*. (Our dining rooms were full during lunchtime.)

Moja porodica i ja smo se uvek veselili *ručku*. (My family and I always looked forward to lunch.)